This paper is about news recommender systems, which are a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL) and natural language processing techniques (cs.CL) to represent news content. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IR, followed by cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, and cs.DL.
